  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/GSS\/gss_krb5_lucid_context_v1\/version\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:44:32Z\n---\n\n# version\n\n**Instance Property**\n\nThe structure version number.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar version: OM_uint32\n```\n\n## Context Members\n\n- **cfx_kd**: The key data structure for Kerberos 5.\n- **endtime**: The expiration time of the context.\n- **initiate**: The flag indicating if the role is initiator.\n- **protocol**: The protocol to use.\n- **recv_seq**: The receive sequence number.\n- **rfc1964_kd**: The RFC-1964 key data.\n- **send_seq**: The send sequence number.\n\n",
